      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，guitool是通用工具库，mtdomegui是MTDome专用模块。继承关系用空心三角，组合关系用实心菱形指向Model。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSelector",
        "Model",
        "guitool",
        "mtdomegui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出两个命名空间，把TabTemplate放进guitool，Model放进mtdomegui，然后建立继承和组合关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabTemplate",
